body:
3D skin analyzer system

3D Skin Analyzer provides facial skin test and morphological analysis to generate customized treatment plan; facial high-definition image data by four spectra can be obtained, Resolution is 2000W Pixel for whole face image; combined with professional skin analysis algorithm, highly referential test reports can be generated; within 8S, 180° high-definition scan on whole face can produce 3D facial modeling; facial Feature Points data can be measured precisely;

#skinanalyzer #3dskinanalyzer #skinanalysis #skinchecking #facechecking #skincare #Sanhebeauty

